All of the `GetEventHandlerValue` methods can be removed, they are unused since we introduced `EventCallback`.
- [x] Remove `GetEventHandlerValue` methods

The `GetValue` methods will be used by `bind` when we need to convert a value to a string. These needs to have some further design iteration. For now we need to answer whether these will be used by user-code or not. I think we need to err on the side of making them usable.
